query:
INSERT INTO skulls (
                "name",
                "color",
                "icon",
                "unit_price",
                "limit"
            ) VALUES (
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                $4,
                $5
            ) RETURNING
                "id" AS "id: types::SkullId",
                "name",
                "color" AS "color: u32",
                "icon",
                "unit_price" AS "unit_price: f32",
                "limit" as "limit: f32"
